; Regression test for issue #1688: Error converting amount with times
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/1688
;
; Using -X $ to convert register output including hour-denominated expenses
; previously caused: "Error: Cannot convert a balance with multiple
; commodities to an amount" when quantity(scrub(display_total)) was called
; on a balance still containing unconverted 'h' amounts.

2018/10/03 Training Flight
    Expenses:Training:Aircraft Rental    1.1h @ $95.00
    Expenses:Training:Flight Instruction  1.1h @ $55.00
    Assets:Checking                     $-165.00

test reg -X $ Expenses
18-Oct-03 Training Flight       Ex:Tra:Aircraft Rental       $60.50       $60.50
                                ..r:Flight Instruction       $60.50      $121.00
end test

test reg -J -X $ Expenses
2018-10-03 60.5
2018-10-03 121
end test
